This paper deals with the distributed management of large corpora of XML documents, which involves aspects of distributed computing, databases, data structures, information retrieval, and networking. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
